Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 你收到过邮局送来的信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是电子邮件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…不多呢 也就是派对的邀请函吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 也就只有那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说电子邮件也很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是实体的信好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如不幸之信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是决斗书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那些吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 新威尼斯快要进入春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连太阳公公也一天一天地…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得暖洋洋的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是白天 也会困意连连…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重啊…亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.73,0:00:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉地就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 谢谢你叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递员老伯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊 白天打盹很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…邮递员老伯看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我从下面看到你在打盹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.02,0:01:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得叫醒你就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天呀 我是以顾客的身份来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢 老伯我的凤尾舟破了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约需要一整天来修理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 我想明天把你们的船包下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来收发邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我马上就去问一下艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:35.96,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那颗 新威尼斯色的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天跟我预约的客人实在太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 小姑娘你来做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 灯里还是见习领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有指导人员在场 是没办法让客人乘坐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的工作能不能找别人代替呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮局的人都说这是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆就休息一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这个与其说是工作 不如说是老伯我的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 我舍不得休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行的话 就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊 委托这么奇怪的工作给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔除了自主练习之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再请一些不同的人来指导怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说 邮递员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是作为指导人员来指导我练习的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 这样小姑娘既能练习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而老伯我也能收发邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一举两得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 社长先生也要一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康纳瑞桥邮政局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里了 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是今天来给邮递员老伯帮忙的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递员老伯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了 好像大家都是邮递员呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 我还不知道老伯的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你就是长老经常提起的那个领航员小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长老？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请里面走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好宏伟的建筑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有墨水的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里是邮局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 小姑娘 你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老伯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么早就让你来 真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一天请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长先生 今天跟老伯戴一样的帽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是早操哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为老伯的工作是体力活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能有点不好意思啦 不过这也是个仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就陪我们做一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递员老伯被称为长老呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也有年轻人管我叫老伯啦 老爹什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 老伯我就是个邮递员老伯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要开始工作了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 靠近点 靠近点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都是如此精准迅速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 要不也来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就试试那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对对对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 放回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全放回原处了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 第一次能这样很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那接下来的慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖力工作过后肚子一定饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个煎蛋卷好好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午还要配送信件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 亚利亚社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 社长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要寄信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这封信 我希望能立刻送到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 今天已经过了收信的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最快也要等到明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不送出去的话就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收信人住很远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那直接放进邮箱不是更快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 因为典礼已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,典礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚典礼？谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这是给老师的祝贺信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面写了「恭贺新婚」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也写了「对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师辞职之前 有一个合唱比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我没有参加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛期间 我一直躲在音乐室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让老师伤透脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在欢送会那天 我甚至还说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「老师不在以后可就轻松了」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时第一次看到老师流泪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那封信给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你送到教堂去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是亚利亚公司的领航员 水无灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小空 真好听的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 赶快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我用逆划过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆划？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就这样一直前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我给你去送信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你 绫乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你幸福 绫乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫乃老师 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有您的信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄信人是小空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 总是给你惹麻烦 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢送会的时候说了这么过分的话 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你说「很轻松」 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…我最喜欢老师你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到你就要离开 就觉得很寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法对你说「恭喜」 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 恭喜你结婚了 要幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送信完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小空真正的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛从信的字里行间传到我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对小空而言 那就是他的最高祝福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对那孩子来说 我是个好老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小空 谢谢你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你回信的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你 老师 要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见 小空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递员伯伯 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 剩下的信件也要赶紧送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一封信送完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新娘子好像很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小空也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递员老伯不舍得休息的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像也有点明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是一份很有意义的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天转了一整天 我才发现到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯有很多邮筒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为这里的人还是习惯于写信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特意做这种麻烦的事 一点都不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢 这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 如果太急了 心情就没法平静下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信这种东西 收到的时候会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开的时候就像打开宝箱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情会变得像孩子一样兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且里面是以书信的形式表现出的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄信人的心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据内容的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时就会变成自己的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成一辈子都能用手触碰到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做「心」的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够用手触碰的「心」…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 信件能跨越时空的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把写信的人带到自己面前来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯城也和信件有相似之处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为创造这座城市的人们的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时都能用双手触碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜欢这个特意做麻烦事的城市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 小姑娘你已经染上新威尼斯的颜色了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 艾莉西亚前辈 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这是今早送来的写给灯里的信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是邮递员老伯寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致小姑娘：
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:21:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递员老伯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.87,0:22:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和邮递员老伯说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信件会把写信的人带到眼前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 那封信虽然很短
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但褪色的墨水字迹却令人感受到浓浓的暖意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面还有邮递员先生那淡淡的烟味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐 你又多了一样宝物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写信啊…说起来我还真的没写过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次试着写写看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样我也能接近新威尼斯的色彩了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份 雨天的精彩…\N那个 春日的发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:14.85,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:27.83,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:42.87,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:55.69,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:55.69,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:03:01.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:09.60,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:17.08,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.61,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:27.39,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:14.85,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:27.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:42.87,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:55.69,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:55.69,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:03:01.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:09.60,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:17.08,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:27.39,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:56.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨が上がる 遠く空眺め 雲の切れ間探す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.99,0:23:08.00,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつもよりも 少し遠回り 海へ続く道を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:15.71,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}切りすぎた前髪 気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:20.31,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そのまま 駆け出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:27.22,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をかすめていく 風の色が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:32.79,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつか夏のはじまりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:39.03,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}大きく手を振って 深呼吸しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:44.64,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}この時間を抱きしめていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:49.77,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}明日もまた会えるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:56.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨过天晴 眺望遥远的天空 探寻云彩的缝隙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.99,0:23:08.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}绕过早已习惯的归途 向着通往大海的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:15.71,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}忘掉剪得过短的留海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:20.31,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}毫无顾忌地大胆前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:27.22,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}吹拂着面颊的海风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:32.79,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不知何时染上了初夏的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:39.03,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}用力挥挥手 来个深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:44.64,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}满心希望永远拥抱这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:49.77,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}明天 我们还会再见吗
